From 07faff368d7fa85715564b0974caf16899f3b5f9 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Chaitanya Kumar Borah <chaitanya.kumar.borah@intel.com>
Date: Thu, 19 Jun 2025 09:56:29 +0530
Subject: drm/xe/display: read PCON capability only when present
Git-commit: 07faff368d7fa85715564b0974caf16899f3b5f9
Patch-mainline: v6.17-rc1
References: jsc#PED-13979 jsc#PED-14039 jsc#PED-14046 jsc#PED-14211 jsc#PED-14333 jsc#PED-14487 jsc#PED-14488 jsc#PED-14497 jsc#PED-14499 jsc#PED-15868

Avoid reading the PCON capabilities redundantly on non-branch devices.

V2: - Make commit description more accurate. (Imre)
 - Clear intel_dp->pcon_dsc_dpcd irrespective of presense of PCON. (Imre)

Signed-off-by: Chaitanya Kumar Borah <chaitanya.kumar.borah@intel.com>
Reviewed-by: Imre Deak <imre.deak@intel.com>
Signed-off-by: Suraj Kandpal <suraj.kandpal@intel.com>
Link: https://lore.kernel.org/r/20250619042629.3980244-1-chaitanya.kumar.borah@intel.com
Acked-by: Patrik Jakobsson <pjakobsson@suse.de>

---
 drivers/gpu/drm/i915/display/intel_dp.c | 3 +++
 1 file changed, 3 insertions(+)

diff --git a/drivers/gpu/drm/i915/display/intel_dp.c b/drivers/gpu/drm/i915/display/intel_dp.c
index b69950319d67..7976fec88606 100644
--- a/drivers/gpu/drm/i915/display/intel_dp.c
+++ b/drivers/gpu/drm/i915/display/intel_dp.c
@@ -3732,6 +3732,9 @@ static void intel_dp_get_pcon_dsc_cap(struct intel_dp *intel_dp)
 
 	memset(intel_dp->pcon_dsc_dpcd, 0, sizeof(intel_dp->pcon_dsc_dpcd));
 
+	if (!drm_dp_is_branch(intel_dp->dpcd))
+		return;
+
 	if (drm_dp_dpcd_read(&intel_dp->aux, DP_PCON_DSC_ENCODER,
 			     intel_dp->pcon_dsc_dpcd,
 			     sizeof(intel_dp->pcon_dsc_dpcd)) < 0)
-- 
